<StandardLayout>

<div style="position: relative;">
  <h1 >Plans</h1>
  <p>All plans contain everything you may need for the core auditing tools such as importing data from your universe of data, pin-point findings, audit, and customizing reports. The Pro and Enterprise tiers are focused on auxiliary features such as automated montioring, etc.</p>
  <p>Every plan is simply a foundation for which you may add or remove features a-la-carte based on your needs.</p>
</div>
  
